oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Norris Lake Auction Layout (16208)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Auctions; Layout (Printing);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing an auction on North Lake near LaFollette on March 29. "North" is crossed out, with "Norris" written above it, "5" crossed out and replaced with "4 1/2", and a typo corrected. To see the business record associated with this poster, visit https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/41499/
